                <h2 class="font-inter font-medium text-black">TELE</h2>
                <p class="font-inter font-light text-gray-700"> Telefon: 036922 4374-0 </p>
                <p class="font-inter font-light text-gray-600"> Telefax: 036922 4374-18 </p>
